data.description: Welcome to this stunning Fountaingrove Home, boasting 4 bedrooms & 3 bathrooms. With its picturesque views & carefully designed layout, this home lives like a single level home.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the inviting vinyl plank flooring, tall cathedral ceilings that allow for an abundance of natural light, further accentuated by recessed lighting & custom chandeliers. The spacious kitchen is a chef's dream equipped w/ new quartz countertops, a serving island, stainless steel appliances, & a delightful breakfast nook. The family room, complete with a gas fireplace, opens up to a private balcony that offers breathtaking views of the city lights of Santa Rosa. Indulge in luxury within the main level primary bedroom, which boasts a walk-in closet with custom built-ins. The elegant, remodeled bathroom showcases a double vanity, custom marble tiling, modern lighting, & a walk-in shower equipped w/ dual shower heads. The lower level of the home comprises a lovely living room & three generously-sized bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation & entertainment. Outside, the low-maintenance yard features Italian cypresses, olive tree & a charming patio area, perfect for grilling & enjoying the outdoors. Newer HVAC system, Tankless W/H, 2 Car Garage. Fantastic Location!
